<subSubSection id="9EECD8B99D21E8101F9B64DB4C70C594" pageId="null" pageNumber="192" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="86C8037AACCDBEAD3F2289AE3CF630C4" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Allionis Ehrenpreis</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="064D449D302C603ECF35261BDD814BAB" pageId="null" pageNumber="192" type="description">
<paragraph id="3A1EF2F3956468AD6CB6751C9D26F128" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="88A86CFB0CF17209B3C05ECA4124BA05" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Plantaginaceae" genus="Veronica" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="192" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="officinalis">
<emphasis id="AD3D171BE11FB1B54F227102A4EE3044" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">V. officinalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 8) durch folgende Merkmale: Bis 10 cm hoch; 
<emphasis id="54014450CDCB6C42F896885814AF1FAF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Stengel am Grunde oft holzig;</emphasis>
Stengel und 
<normalizedToken id="F8646AB1DB26051E4C0EFEF7F6AFA9EB" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
kahl; 
<emphasis id="830A0F7C1B7823A08FA5A526E91E7CB6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">
<normalizedToken id="1749E86EF115630178EABD6ED3310911" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
klein, 
<normalizedToken id="9BB2CAAA2F04475787A6B4AEA9A5E268" originalValue="höchstens" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">hoechstens</normalizedToken>
1,5 cm lang
</emphasis>
, 1- 
<normalizedToken id="CC40217A7C10BDABC55A5494CFFE7D15" originalValue="1½" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">11/2</normalizedToken>
mal so lang wie breit, oft undeutlich 
<normalizedToken id="1026D194DD4041AB9800BD4B11205BCD" originalValue="gezähnt" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">gezaehnt</normalizedToken>
, lederig; 
<normalizedToken id="E05A9FC931E8DF9BDDDC894B231B5BBC" originalValue="Blütenstandsstiele" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Bluetenstandsstiele</normalizedToken>
mit kurzen, 
<normalizedToken id="474D6C34B8D7AD8DB7681CA78B493774" originalValue="aufwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">aufwaerts</normalizedToken>
gebogenen Haaren; 
<emphasis id="E578D55B6B5502FA3B9E4746810988F9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">
<normalizedToken id="F1AE20D317EEAA3ED2320FCF1ECA8B76" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Blueten</normalizedToken>
zu 30
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="DF4D995CAC4483A31684B353CA239D7B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">
60 in einer sehr dichten 
<normalizedToken id="AFD1EC810A5D95EDF550A3E73D270CC5" originalValue="Ähre" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Aehre</normalizedToken>
; Krone im Durchmesser 7
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="785974301B3654A02E6C96BF044B04F7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">9 mm, himmelblau;</emphasis>
Staubbeutel 2-2,5 mm lang; Frucht 2-3 mm lang, 
<normalizedToken id="4F16C2E88D7BF86383138083956F92BB" originalValue="länger" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">laenger</normalizedToken>
als breit; Griffel 1- 
<normalizedToken id="A7D63B56D4BB223FA09BB4E35DF08D3D" originalValue="1½" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">11/2</normalizedToken>
mal so lang wie die Frucht. - 
<normalizedToken id="21F8F6908A7CA6AB468C3CAA46D0DFF0" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="ED9ABE4147F749933E69DBD637601F0F" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">
<emphasis id="38C86A7C6C6A68C67AB92F740FF18952" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="88EC850209450E8F1A16C13F6F7799BA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">18:</emphasis>
Material aus den Westalpen (Bocquet et al. 1967).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7FE0AE305AA6AA591A4EED4E582E1481" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">
<emphasis id="4F4CE1E7C7E1B9983EDBFC4B709D0A76" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Standort</emphasis>
. Subalpin, seltener alpin. Trockene, steinige, humose, meist kalkarme 
<normalizedToken id="0843651C6509FF6A0D44E2EC2F9AA66F" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. Waldlichtungen, 
<normalizedToken id="0834D6EE53B7859FC92CADCEBB16B886" originalValue="Waldränder" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Waldraender</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="FFB69A632E9186190915BECEA2E1DB49" originalValue="Hänge" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Haenge</normalizedToken>
, Weiden.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="72C3902BE03687BDD42FA780E9ACBF23" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">
<emphasis id="1D4DE214E3A66E5E38A99A77FFF6A099" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Verbreitung. Westalpen-Pflanze:</emphasis>
Westalpen (
<normalizedToken id="5A687408F140F957F16323636DA92E22" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis zum Col 
<normalizedToken id="876468BB88F130CF00FC1445E8992AB7" originalValue="d’Iséran" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">d'Iseran</normalizedToken>
). - Im Gebiet: Savoyen und Aostatal (von St-Sorlin 
<normalizedToken id="5F7B0A6C9F2D8DC31F855C467F26EA65" originalValue="d’Arves" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">d'Arves</normalizedToken>
und vom Col de la Galise 
<normalizedToken id="78195258EFC93D677777CAE44FB05E78" originalValue="südwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">suedwaerts</normalizedToken>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
